{"tid":1761071,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺好多人想等poly解封就入去救手足，我有少少忠告","createTime":"2019-11-28T15:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T20:52:54.000Z","uid":37971,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f1483b6a6d8271be440cea8f30bf4fa6414584a2","tid":1761071,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">小心黑警再包抄</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n啲曱甴咁蠱惑，唔知會唔會等一大班人入去<br />\n再用非法集結做理由，又玩大圍捕<br />\n<br />\n大量手足入去我唔反對，但係真係要小心埋呢點<br />\n解決方法：<br />\n除咗多哨，入去嘅都要密切留意哨台<br />\ntg唔夠快嘅就用zello<br />\n手足要識be water<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">記住不被捕係最大原則</span><br />\n<br />\n各位手足 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8c3cd51ee58b0797e7a07536a3a182fd1a115c","tid":1761071,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T15:52:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee544cddbb6882a6b921bb4039046681bc964ff7","tid":1761071,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T15:52:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9bc87993a9a66fd26af9822584452a9b0bdadc3","tid":1761071,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T15:53:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2467726fa6e190333ebe7fa7ba719672f7e0e582","tid":1761071,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T15:53:46.000Z","msg":"真係無用post就由佢沉啦&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"56e9342f892dab2f8a1f18f57fb3292851669da9","tid":1761071,"uid":47479,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T15:54:04.000Z","msg":"學校入面點告非法集結<br />\n不過好似話就算開放返都只係比學生同staff入?<br />\n咁和理非手足入去就OK啦<br />\n大條道理入學校"},{"pid":"d27bcf9b667f11a26d55ea94dedd61806db3fd33","tid":1761071,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56e9342f892dab2f8a1f18f57fb3292851669da9","tid":1761071,"uid":47479,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11